text: Newly opened here. Not all stalls are occupied yet. There's Tze Char, Vegetarian, Wonton noodles, Carrot cake/fried rice and economic rice stalls here. Will be good to see Malay, Indian options added. Will get a bit crowded during lunch but still able to get tables. Once there are more tenants will get even more crowded.
Food sucks. Limited choices as some stalls already closed down ?! Some stalls only accept cash. Some areas no connection for paynow.

Favourite stalls 德福21猪脚面 and Po Chuan are previously from Defu Lane canteen
猪脚面 pork trotter noodles (or rice) well cooked, soft and flavoursome n usually will pack some home also
Call 98635507 to reserve otherwise sold out quickly
Quite rare to have egg noodles with pork trotters
Po Chuan fried rice is simple and not oily
